## OWASP Top 10 Mapping

| OWASP Category | Vulnerability | Severity |
|---------------|---------------|----------|
| A01:2021 Broken Access Control | Missing auth/authorization | High |
| A02:2021 Cryptographic Failures | Weak token generation | High |
